metadata.name: Flight
metadata.description:
As a child he believed he could fly. Looking to the sky he was one of them.
Would life lift him up to all his dreams or would he be grounded by its harsh reality.

This is the first of ten pieces in the Dream, Ego, Legacy collection.

Two Families: 
The Edmonds Family
The Bryant Family

Young Walt is the first of 5 and the youngest in the Edmonds family.

1 of 10
Artist: Bennett
